<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8253648>
    dc:description "PLATE 2. General schemes of the chorion in Hypanartia.A. Regionalization of the chorion in lateral view; B. Three-dimensional model for the ridges in Nymphalinae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8253648/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8253660>
    dc:description "PLATE 6. Chorion of Hypanartia bella. A. Lateral view; B. Apical view. i=ridges in colonnade; ii=short ridges; iii= apical columns; iv= intercolumnar space; v= ‘falling’ ridges; vi= reduced columns; vii=apical ribs; viii=basal ribs; ix= vestigial ‘ribs’." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8253660/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8253666>
    dc:description "PLATE8. ChorionofHypanartialethe.A.Lateralview;B.Apicalview.i=ridgeincolonnade;ii=apicalcolumns;iii=intercolumnar wall; iv=basal ribs; v=vestigial ribs." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8253666/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8253668>
    dc:description "PLATE 9. Photographs of the chorion of Hypanartia lethe under the SEM.A Lateral view.; B. Detail of the colonnades; C. Basal region; D. Apical view; E. Perimicropylar region; F. Micropyle." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8253668/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8253672>
    dc:description "PLATE 10. Chorion of Hypanartia godmanii. A. Lateral view; B. Apical view. i=ridge in colonnades; ii= apical columns; iii= apical ribs; iv=basal ribs; v =intercolumnar walls; vi=projections of the ridges in the transition zone." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8253672/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8253674>
    dc:description "PLATE 11. Photographs of the chorion of Hypanartia godmanii under the SEM. A Lateral view.; B. Detail of the colonnades; C. Basal region; D. Apical view; E. Perimicropylar region; F. Micropyle." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8253674/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8253692>
    dc:description "PLATE 17. Morphology of the complete ridges of eight genera of Nymphalini. Representations in lateral view. The order of the genera is by morphological proximity of the ridges." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8253692/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8253696>
    dc:description "PLATE 18. Anatomy of the components of the most apical section of the ridges in eight genera of Nymphalinae. The order of the genera is by morphological proximity of the ridges." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8253696/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8253678>
    dc:description "PLATE 12. Chorion of Hypanartia dione disjunct. A. Lateral view; B. Apical view. i=ridges in colonnade; ii=apical columns longer than equatorial ones; iii=intercolumnar spacing; iv=basal ribs; v=projections of the ridges in the transition zone." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8253678/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8253682>
    dc:description "PLATE 13. Photographs of the chorion of Hypanartia dione disjuncta under the SEM. A Lateral view.; B. Detail of the colonnades; C. Basal region; D. Apical view; E. Perimicropylar region; F. Micropyle." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8253682/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8253686>
    dc:description "PLATE 14. Chorion of Hypanartia trimaculata autumn. A. Lateral view; B. Apical view. i=ridges in colonnade; ii= apical columns overhanging the surface; iii=reduced ridges (beam only); iv=vestigial ’ribs’; v=intercolumnar spacing; vi=basal ribs; vii= projections of the ridges in the transition zone." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8253686/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8253688>
    dc:description "PLATE 15. Photographs of the chorion of Hypanartia trimaculata autumn under the SEM. A Lateral view.; B. Detail of the colonnades; C. Basal region; D. Apical view; E. Perimicropylar region; F. Micropyle." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8253688/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8253690>
    dc:description "PLATE 16. Comparative dendrogram of ridges in Hypanartia spp. (redrawn from the cladogram of Willmott et al. 2001). Two species of Antanartia have been added. *=hyper-development of the ridges by elongated fusts." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8253690/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8253662>
    dc:description "PLATE 7. Photographs of the chorion of Hypanartia bella under the SEM. A Lateral view.; B. Detail of the colonnades; C. Basal region; D. Apical view; E. Perimicropylar region; F. Micropyle." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8253662/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8253698>
    dc:description "PLATE 19. Arrangement and thickness of columns A. Double arrangement with slender columns and small zig-zag aeropyles. B. Simple arrangement with thick columns, large aeropyles in a straight line." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8253698/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8253700>
    dc:description "PLATE 20. Modifications in the beam in the Nymphalini. A. Straight beam; B. Arched beam." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8253700/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

